    "### 1.\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "xGD can dictate which team wins\n",
    "\n",
    "True xGD:\n",
    "if xGD and xGA both have the same sign ('+ +' or '- -'):\n",
    "= xGD - (xG vs Actual)\n",
    "\n",
    "if xGD and xGA have opposite signs:\n",
    "= xGD + (xGA vs Actual)\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "Tottenham true xGD = -0.06\n",
    "Aston Villa true xGD = -0.06\n",
    "\n"
